commentTextItems.html: good length delivery just outside off stump, Duminy drives to the cover fence and wraps the series in style

commentPostTextItems.html: South Africa have reached the target in style within 28 overs and have wrapped the series in the 3-match ODI series. Please join us for the last and final match. Cheers and bye!

commentTextItems.html: short of length ball just outside off stump, pushed to cover
short ball outside off stump, cut away to thirdman
straight full toss, Duminy drives through the off side wide of the deep cover fielder
full on the stumps, Duminy drives on the front foot
